data.description: Charming 3 bedroom 2 full & 1 and a half bathroom ranch set in the Foxon neighborhood. As you enter the home you'll be drawn to the brick fireplace with beautiful built in bookcases on either side, the living room opens up to the spacious eat-in kitchen with beautiful breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, and sliding door leading out to the back deck. Also on the main level is the large primary bedroom with private half bathroom, the two remaining bedrooms are generously sized with ample closet space. The lower level has plenty of opportunity for you to come in and put your own finishing touching on the space as it has been partially finished and features a full bathroom and space that would make a nice additional family/ game room, or home gym. This home is within 10 minutes of Lake Saltonstall which offers fishing, hiking, and walking trails. It is also conveniently located close to shops and restaurants and is close to both I-91 & I-95. Call to schedule your showing today! *Seller is having the retaining wall rebuilt as well as repairing the front steps.
